    Download the CPI series

    get_ipc_data.Rd

    Download the CPI inflacion series for the Dominican Republic in any disaggregation

    Usage

    get_ipc_data(desagregacion)

    Arguments

    desagregacion

    string with the desired disaggregation. options: "general", "grupos", "regiones", "subyacente", "tnt" (transable y no transable), "articulos"

    Value

    a tibble

    Examples

    get_ipc_data("general")
